          The
          <span
            class="w-full text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 via-blue-400 to-purple-400 lg:inline"
            >Challenge</span
          >
          of
          <span
            class="w-full text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 via-blue-400 to-purple-400 lg:inline"
            >Launching your own MVP</span
          >
        </Trans>
      </h1>
      <Trans i18nKey="hero.description">
        <p class="text-gray-300 sm:text-xl md:mt-5 lg:text-2xl md:max-w-4xl font-normal max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
          Launching an MVP (Minimum Viable Product) is a monumental task,
          especially for solopreneurs !
        </p>
